VAERS report 1288833:
47yo Female, North Carolina
Found unresponsive at home 12 days after Pfizer vaccination. Declared dead in the home.

Why was this report removed from VAERS after 08-27-2021?

.@JoeNBC .@Morning_Joe I live in a North Carolina County with almost 30% of Covid tests positive, less than 60% vaccination rate and the average age of Covid patients is 36. The school board just lifted the mask mandate.
That one time I briefly followed the North Carolina Polyamory FB group and found it full of anti-vaccination and blue lives matter people. I should have known better.
